name: Another side
description:
In the subconscious, we are carried away in angels and evil spirits. We all hide behind the wings of kindness. The evil spirit that always instigates us to continue to sin, the lust of the world that we always pursue, envy and hatred also unwittingly grow within us. But we only show our beauty to them, no matter what sin we have committed.

This artwork is made in digital form measuring 3000 x 3000 px
